citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 12:00pm on 15-
DEC-2022.
The inspectors arrived at the facility at 12 PM. We rang the doorbells to the house, called the phone number and left a
message, and drove to the entrance of the kennel and honked the horn. The inspector spoke to the facility representative
on the phone who stated no one was available for the inspection. The inspectors then left the facility.
Additional Inspectors:
KELLY MAXWELL, ANIMAL CARE INSPECTOREnd Section
